Class SyncMsgTableModel

java.lang.Object
  |

        +--edu.tamu.gamebots.ui.SyncMsgTableModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, TableModel
public class SyncMsgTableModel
extends AbstractTableModel

A table model for displaying vision messages from the server based on a MessageBlock object. Columns:

  • Column 1: Type
  • Column 2: ID
  • Column 3: Location
  • Column 4: Reachable (Boolean)
